item.content:encoded:
black-and-blue-fancomic:Anonymous asked black-and-blue-fancomic:

Sneefee, maybe this will upset you or make you mad but please show us the Valentine R/L mini comics. I’ve been following your art since the very beginning and let me tell you, your art was and still is beautiful! You don’t need to be ashamed of your first drawings. The “old fans” would love to see those no matter how old they are; 5 years, 10 years… it doesn’t matter! Besides, it’s better to see them here rather than elsewhere coming from an art thief.

—-

Guuuh hit me right in the feels why don’t you XD I got so many asks requesting me to post them and I was gonna be all stubborn and ignore them but gaaah. I’m weak. XD

“Enjoy”, I guess. XD So oooold aaaaaah. 

This is the second year I did a V-day comic, in 2009. The 2008 comic is here
